             was indicted for <rs id="t17821204-5-off24" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17821204-5-off24" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17821204-5-off24" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17821204-5-victim96" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Williams
                        <interp inst="t17821204-5-victim96" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
