                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821204-5-off24 t17821204-5-victim96"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , at the hour of ten in the night, on the <rs id="t17821204-5-cd25" type="crimeDate">29th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821204-5-off24 t17821204-5-cd25"></join> last, and stealing therein a silk handkerchief, value 2 s. nine yards of silk, value 40 s. one metal watch, value 3 l. one worked muslin apron, value 30 s. one silver pint mug, value 40 s. one pair of muslin ruffles, value 5 s. two silver salts, value 20 s. one silver pap spoon, value 8 s. and one garnet ring, value 8 s. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17821204-5-person97">
                        William
                         Williams
                     <interp inst="t17821204-5-person97" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
